'''Hadan''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0647><U+0627><U+062F><U+0627><U+0646>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''H<U+0101>d<U+0101>n''' and '''Had<U+0101>n'''; also known as '''Ard<U+016B>n''', '''H<U+0101>d<U+016B>n''', and '''H<U+0101>v<U+0101>n''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3065319|Hadan}}</ref> is a village in [[Sardshir Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Buin va Miandasht County)|Central District]] of [[Buin va Miandasht County]], [[Isfahan Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 498, in 115 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|10}}</ref>  

